块链，即联盟链等就不需要挖矿，所以你可以设计为有交易时再出块，也可以设计为可以出空块。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1649491220,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":335347,"user_name":"黄矢","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1136224,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7ADD89AB9380AD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/56/60/fb5ca9e5.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1645460108,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1645460108","product_id":100084201,"comment_content":"状态相当于执行一系列操作后，显示的一个目前的状态，让人一目了然，我认为区块更重要，因为对区块的应用更多，更有价值","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":318540,"user_name":"^_^","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1261604,"ip_address":"","ucode":"9BF0C1443A957A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/40/24/8bd1af8b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1635326952,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"115506","content":"不可篡改是针对的多方中的任意少数主体对数据的私自修改，有共识算法保证对数据的私自修改不会影响整个网络的状态，且一般情况下所有的参与方权利与义务是等同的。而数据库一般的主体是同一个，很少有多方共同使用一个数据库的情况，就算这种情况存在，设置控制权限实质是将参与方进行了分级，性质有所改变。你可以从数据库参与方的权利义务相同的角度考虑这个问题。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"自游","uid":"1063942","ctime":1635347390,"ip_address":"","comment_id":318540,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1635326952","product_id":100084201,"comment_content":"为什么说数据库不具备不可篡改性？我觉得应该是对于区块链篡改成本更高？数据库也是可以通过设置控制权限的啊","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1063942,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/3c/06/977c1e92.jpg","nickname":"自游","note":"","ucode":"5DE116D6A44139","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":529291,"discussion_content":"不可篡改是针对的多方中的任意少数主体对数据的私自修改，有共